Files vendored
--------------

  d_ms.cs   src/FFXI Navmesh Builder/Common/dat/Types/d_ms.cs
            Contains the zone-id -> ROM DAT file-id formula used by
            `ParseD_MSG` to wire each zone's collision DAT into the
            navmesh builder. The relevant line is

                var fileId = x < 256 ? x + 100 : x + 83635;

            where `x` is the zone-id. This formula is what `ffxi-dat`'s
            `build.rs` parses out at compile time to generate the
            static zone-id -> file-id lookup table.

